node.text: Hey guys - this is one of my favorite exercises that I love to hate.  You can do this against a bed or a shelf, and it really works your body in a way that you're going to love/hate too!  Give this a shot people.

node.text:
When Ben and I started @be_more_athletics our goal was to help change lives and create a positive community.
The last 5 years at Be More Athletics have been so precious to me. So many memories made, friendships formed and lives changed. Each one special and unique and for that I will always be thankful.

Unfortunately due to the new laws, rules and regulations Be More Athletics will not be reopening after the Covid-19 Shutdown. 💔

We want to give a special THANK YOU and so much love to our talented trainers @metta_world_hayden @keepfit_11 @valeriaalmendaro  @aj.yumul @clintonious_ @yetitube @shaynaholt 
Without you Be More Athletics wouldn’t have been the same.
We want to thank all of our members and anyone who has ever come out to take a class, Bootcamp or just to support us. I’ll forever be grateful to my Be More Athletics Family you changed my life, thank you.

#Gym #BeMoreAthletics #Family #community

My 2 Tips For This Rosy Look 👀 .

1) Blend out the shadow first and add more if you want a darker pigment.
2) Press the brow setter in and up with your finger for a laminated looking brow! It will stay all day 🙌🏼 .
.

Eyes:
@lauramercier Caviar Sticks in the color Violet and Rose Gold

.

node.text:
Hi everyone! 
This is my signature look, especially the eyes 👀 the tips I would give you to help recreate my style are:

1) To keep it glowy I only set with translucent powder at the inner corners of my under eyes, in between my brows and my smile lines.

2) When doing a wing liner with eyeshadow be sure your brush is flat, skinny and sharp to get a good clean line.

3) only add the lash clusters on the outer corners of your eyes to help lift and elongate for a snatched cat eye!

The products I used are @tartecosmetics 💜 and in order:

Maracuja Oil (for the glowglow)

Maracuja Tinted Hydrator in the shade 36S
(It’s slightly dark for me atm but still blends, I was matched when I was still tan)

Shape Tape Wonder Wand in the shade Aglow
(This is my favorite right now to brighten! But FYI it’s not meant to be a concealer)

The Maneater Palette (consistently using this palette and haven’t hit pan yet 🏆) Maneater Mascara (Hands down this is my FAVORITE mascara EVER!) Blush in shade B-Day Bae from the Cue the Confetti party collection

Lipstick in the shade Siesta

Stay Spray

Oh and the lashes I used are @ardellbeauty lash Trio 👌🏼 #gifted 
#beauty #tartecosmetics #tarte #tarteshapetape #maracuja #makeup #glam #cateyes #quarantine #quarantinelife #mua #happyathome #glow #glowingskin
